attributionInfo.brokerName: Main Street Realty of Pueblo, Inc

data.description: Rare opportunity to own this solidly built ranch-style home right in the middle of the desirable Desert Hawk at Pueblo West Golf Course. Peaceful location with gorgeous mountain views to provide a warm welcome home. Nice covered tiled front porch perfect for a couple chairs and potted plants. The spacious living room features a corner fireplace and a large picture window. Formal dining room perfect for hosting large gatherings, and an eat-in kitchen great for everyday living. Three generous-sized bedrooms with the primary located opposite the guest bedrooms for added privacy and has dual mirrored closets and convenient en-suite bath. Enclosed back porch makes a great sunroom. Full 1,150 sq. ft. unfinished basement ready to finish off for more living space or use for storage. Peaceful backyard with ample mature trees and frequent wildlife visitors. Ideally located just minutes to several dining options, Pueblo Public Library, and quick access to Pueblo Reservoir and I-25.
